stucson.org/worship-services/|title=St. Michael and All Angels Episcopal Church in Tucson|website=https://smallangelstucson.org/|access-date=2019-10-18}}</ref>\n| \n|-\n|[[St. Thomas the Apostle Hollywood]]\n| Los Angeles, California \n|\n|self-identifies as Anglo Catholic<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.saintthomashollywood.org/html/|title=St. Thomas the Apostle, Hollywood}}</ref> weekly Rosary,weekly Mass in Latin<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.saintthomashollywood.org/html/rectors-corner/liturgy/|title=St. Thomas the Apostle, Hollywood \u00bb Liturgy}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| All Saints Parish\n|San Diego, California\n|\n|self Identifies as Anglo-Catholic<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allsaintschurch.org/|title=Welcome to All Saints' Episcopal Church - San Diego Sermon Page|website=www.allsaintschurch.org}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|All Saints Episcopal Church\n|Haight-Ashbury, San Francisco, California\n|\n|Self-identifies as Progressive and Inclusive Anglo-Catholic; seasonal Daily Office; Week-day Mass MWF, Solemn High Mass with incense, chanted prayers and traditional vestments.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://allsaintssf.org/|title=All Saints' Episcopal Church San Francisco|website=All Saints' Episcopal Church San Francisco|language=en|access-date=2020-01-29}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|Church of the Advent of Christ the King\n|San Francisco, California\n|\n|Self identifies as Anglo-Catholic, Daily Masses, Latin Mass<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.advent-sf.org/|title=Church of the Advent of Christ the King &#124; San Francisco, CA|website=Church of the Advent}}</ref><ref>http://advent-sf.org/services-and-events</ref>\n|\n|-\n|St. Mary's Anglican Catholic Church\n|Denver, Colorado\n|\n|Uses the 1928 Book of Common Prayer along with the Anglican Missal (per website),<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.saintmarysacc.org/worship/|title=Mass Times {{!}} St. Marys Anglican Catholic Church|website=www.saintmarysacc.org|access-date=2019-05-23}}</ref> and emphasizes elements of faith and practice associated wi