n by police and army in Malaysia during MCO.jpg|thumb|220px|Joint inspection by the [[Royal Malaysia Police|police]] and [[Malaysian Army|army]] during the enhanced [[2020 Malaysia movement control order|movement control order]] in Malaysia.]]\n[[File:CRPF trooper during Curfew.png|thumb|Officer of the [[Central Armed Police Forces]] during national COVID-19 curfew in India.]]\n[[File:High Street and Curfew Tower, Cushendall, Co. Antrim - geograph.org.uk - 1381257.jpg|thumb|Empty street in Cushendall, [[Northern Ireland]]]]\n[[File:6954Baliuag enhanced community quarantine 37.jpg|thumb|2020 [[Curfew Pass]] in Baliuag, Phillippines.]]\n[[File:Mahane Yehuda Market closed in coronavirus outbreak.jpg|thumb|Mahane Yehuda Market in Jerusalem.]]\n[[File:Policemen wearing masks patrolling Wuhan Tianhe Airport during Wuhan coronavirus outbreak.jpg|thumb|Policemen wearing masks patrolling Wuhan Tianhe Airport during Wuhan coronavirus outbreak (22 January 2020)]]\n\n==Type of regulation by country==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed style=\"font-size:80%;\"\n|-\n! Country !! Main article !! Type of regulation !! Start date !! Expiry date{{efn|Curfews or lockdowns may be extended. The date listed for the lifting of ongoing restrictions is the latest reported date.}}!! References\n|-\n|{{ALB}} || ||nationwide curfew from 13:00 to 05:00 on Mondays to Saturdays<br>full lockdown on Sundays ||{{Date table sorting|March 13}} || || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://de.reuters.com/article/health-coronavirus-albania-curfew/albanians-begin-life-under-daily-curfew-as-coronavirus-cases-rise-idINL8N2BG91I|title=Albanians begin life under daily curfew as coronavirus cases rise|last=|first=|date=23 March 2020|website=Reuters|language=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{DZA}} || ||curfew in the capital city from 19:00 to 07:00, full lockdown in [[Blida]]<br>curfew expanded to 15:00 to 07:00 in capital city and eight other provinces, 19:00