53FW |website=Reuters |language=en |date=18 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{TUR}} || [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Turkey]] || curfew for under 20 aged people and over 65 aged <ref>{{cite web |title=Soka\u011fa \u00e7\u0131kma yasa\u011f\u0131 ya\u015f aral\u0131\u011f\u0131 nedir? |url=https://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/sokaga-cikma-yasagi-yas-araligi-nedir-sokaga-cikma-yasagi-cezasi-ne-kadar-41489708|date=10 April 2020|website=Hurriyet |language=tr}}</ref>, stay-at-home lockdown in 31 cities from 2020-04-11 until 2020-04-12<ref>{{cite web |title= Son dakika haberi: 31 \u015fehirde soka\u011fa \u00e7\u0131kma yasa\u011f\u0131 resmen ba\u015flad\u0131! \u0130\u015fte soka\u011fa \u00e7\u0131kma yasa\u011f\u0131ndan muaf olacaklar |url= https://www.hurriyet.com.tr/gundem/son-dakika-haberi-icisleri-bakanligi-duyurdu-30-buyuksehir-ve-zonguldakta-48-saat-sokaga-cikma-yasagi-41491927|date=10 April 2020|website=Hurriyet |language=tr}}</ref> stay-at-home lockdown in 31 cities from 2020-04-18 until 2020-04-20 ||{{Date table sorting|11 April 2020}} || {{Date table sorting|12 April 2020}} ||<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/04/turkey-imposes-48-hour-lockdown-major-cities-curb-virus-200411084517572.html|title=Turkey imposes 48-hour curfew in major cities to curb virus|website=www.aljazeera.com}}</ref>\n|-\n|{{UAE}} || || stay-at-home lockdown, curfew from 06:00 to 20:00 h except for Dubai city which has 24 h curfew||  || ||<ref name=\"auto\"/>\n|-\n|{{UK}} || [[2020 United Kingdom coronavirus lockdown|2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United Kingdom]] || stay-at-home instruction || {{Date table sorting|March 23}} || {{Date table sorting|May 7}} || <ref>{{cite news |title=Coronavirus: Strict new curbs on life in UK announced by PM |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-52012432 |accessdate=25 March 2020 |work=BBC |date=24 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dw.com/en/coronavirus-latest-uk-rolls-out-nationwide-lockdown/a-52882909 |title=Coronavirus lates